we saw the Hamilton app

00:01:35.250 --> 00:01:37.890
ship, when we saw that team
be successful with Flutter.

00:01:37.890 --> 00:01:39.990
We'd seen teams be
successful inside Google

00:01:39.990 --> 00:01:42.240
for several years.

00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:45.870
