we had much less ability

00:01:45.870 --> 00:01:49.650
to talk to on a
minute to minute basis

00:01:49.650 --> 00:01:51.720
be successful with
this technology,

00:01:51.720 --> 00:01:54.059
helped me believe that,
yeah, anybody can use this.

00:01:54.059 --> 00:01:55.350
MARTIN AGUINIS: That was great.

00:01:55.350 --> 00:01:57.330
I know now they have
over a million installs,

00:01:57.330 --> 00:01:59.460
and a lot of people
are winning tickets

00:01:59.460 --> 00:02:01.330
through that app or $10 tickets.

00:02:01.330 --> 00:02:02.520
So that's really great.

00:02:02.520 --> 00:02:04.562
