headed in the future?

00:02:04.562 --> 00:02:05.936
ERIC SEIDEL: So
one of the things

00:02:05.936 --> 00:02:07.350
that we're seeing
with Flutter is

00:02:07.350 --> 00:02:11.360
we're seeing people take
Flutter to more places.

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:13.410
We started with
I was in Android,

00:02:13.410 --> 00:02:16.620
because that's where so
many developers are today.

00:02:16.620 --> 00:02:19.110
But we've seen people
bring Flutter to desktop.

00:02:19.110 --> 00:02:21.180
We've seen people
experiment with Flutter

00:02:21.180 --> 00:02:24.480
